metadata.name: Citizens of Galaxy #1
metadata.description: Citizens of Galaxy is an NFT project that aims to provide multiple benefits to its holders. The first feature of the project is that it is the main collection of NFT Base, which is a company that has many projects from the sports industry to the clothing industry. Apart from that, Citizens of Galaxy, the world's first team play based NFT treasure hunt project, is a candidate to be one of the most comprehensive metaverses in the world with the omnichain, in game workshop and office systems it will bring with support of its massive partners. Simpler systems such as stake to earn, breeding, raffles, alpha access, WL spots are also included in the project.
